(ooc: that's ok, jerry :)

Element watched with satisfaction while Tantrum flew off and landed near 
Rampage. He grunted, remembering that those bots were never any good. 
Element turned around and saw Divebomb throwing two bombs at the CF. Two 
laser rifles on his shoulders fired a few times and managed to destroy one 
of the bombs.

He growled and turned to Divebomb. "Get out of here or face me, Decepticon." 
said Element in a deep voice while two missiles left his missile launchers 
and headed for the robot he was talking with.
